Purpose. The TGOSC forwards recommendations through DCS, G-3/5/7 (Training Directorate) for
decision by the appropriate Army leaders (DCS, G-3/5/7; Vice Chief of Staff of the Army (VCSA); CSA;
Assistant Secretary of the Army (Manpower and Reserve Affairs) (ASA (M&RA)); and SECARMY).

Officer. Basic Officer Leader Course (BOLC A), US Military Academy (USMA), Reserve Officer
Training Corps (ROTC), Officer Candidate School (OCS), and Direct Commission Course (DCC) and
BOLC B).;
